## Quick Reference — Most Used Commands

| Task | Command |
|------|---------|
| Pull image | `docker pull nginx:alpine` |
| Run detached | `docker run -d --name app -p 8080:80 nginx` |
| View logs | `docker logs app` |
| Shell into container | `docker exec -it app sh` |
| Stop & remove | `docker stop app; docker rm app` |
| Build image | `docker build -t myapp:1.0 .` |
| Compose up | `docker compose up -d` |
| Maven build | `mvn clean verify` |

